Comment: 0,0:14:16.91,0:14:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Er...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.12,0:00:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Tomoe Mami.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.67,0:00:17.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like you, I'm a third year student at Mitakihara City Middle School.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.38,0:00:25.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Additionally, I'm a Magical Girl who has signed a contract with Kyubei.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.88,0:00:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Another weird dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.05,0:00:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Madoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.61,0:02:17.36,EPISODE TITLE,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\bord0\an1\fad(236,0)\c&H6B6E73&\pos(338,489)}Episode 2   That would be very nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.61,0:02:17.36,EPISODE TITLE,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(236,0)\pos(334,483)}Episode 2   That would be very nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.82,0:02:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard you got home really late last night, Madoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.33,0:02:37.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My senior invited me over to her house.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.46,0:02:42.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to tell you when to come home,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.74,0:02:44.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but at least try to call me before dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.87,0:02:46.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.96,0:02:57.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess he really {\i1}is{\i0} invisible to others.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.49,0:03:17.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a wonderful house!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.09,0:03:19.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to act so formal. I live here alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.68,0:03:22.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have much to offer in the way of hospitality though.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.01,0:03:29.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's delicious, Mami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.77,0:03:31.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so tasty, I'm gonna explode!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.25,0:03:32.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.86,0:03:37.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You two are no longer strangers to me after being chosen by Kyubei.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.73,0:03:40.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to explain some important things to you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.40,0:03:43.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just ask whatever you'd like to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.16,0:03:44.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the opposite, Sayaka-chan. {TLC Note: "That's the opposite."}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.24,0:03:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.35,0:03:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a Soul Gem. {TLC Note: "Soul Gem"}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.00,0:03:55.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a precious stone, born out of the contract formed between Kyubei and a chosen girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.81,0:04:00.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a source of magical power and proof of a Magical Girl's identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.26,0:04:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the contract?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.52,0:04:05.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can fulfill one of your wishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.23,0:04:07.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.17,0:04:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wishes... Meaning?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.60,0:04:12.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can be anything, I'll be able to grant it, no matter how miraculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.45,0:04:18.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like riches, long life, something like great food?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.77,0:04:20.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That last one is a little...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.99,0:04:24.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, in doing so, a Soul Gem {TLC Note: "Soul Gem"}will be created.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.03,0:04:28.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The receiver of the stone becomes obligated to fight Witches as a Magical Girl. {TLC NOTE:  "will be required to fight Witches"?} {TL: << as a Magical Girl}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.61,0:04:30.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Witches?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.92,0:04:37.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Mama?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.59,0:04:38.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.81,0:04:41.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What if, just if,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.50,0:04:45.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,someone told you that you could use magic to fulfill one wish,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.75,0:04:46.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,what would you—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.49,0:04:49.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd wish for my two managers to screw around somewhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.10,0:04:52.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What else, let me think...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.04,0:04:56.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The CEO isn't young anymore,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.39,0:04:59.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish he would consider retiring.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.39,0:05:01.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there's no one to replace him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.73,0:05:05.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you become the CEO then?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.24,0:05:09.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's always that possibility, isn't there?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.92,0:05:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once we've dealt with the sales department,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.80,0:05:16.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Corporate Planning and the General Manager will be easy to manipulate.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.30,0:05:19.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, the problem lies with that bald-headed manager. {TL: Added in}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.01,0:05:21.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll just do it this way and pull our hair out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.17,0:05:24.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your eyes look really scary, Mama.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.97,0:05:30.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are Witches, are they different from Magical Girls?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.55,0:05:33.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Magical Girls are born from wishes,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.91,0:05:36.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then Witches are born from curses.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.44,0:05:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magical girls help fulfill wishes, while Witches spread despair.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.30,0:05:45.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's more, they can't be seen by normal people. They are really evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.83,0:05:52.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anxiety and suspicion, rage and hate, they bring such seeds of discord into the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.62,0:05:59.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unreasonable suicides and killings primarily stem from the curses of Witches.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.42,0:06:05.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This unseen enemy has begun to move against the hearts of the people.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.01,0:06:08.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If such dangerous people exist, why doesn't anyone know about them?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.95,0:06:14.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Witches have always remained hidden and would never reveal themselves to anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.16,0:06:18.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The maze-like structure you were trapped in before is a reality marble. {TLC Note: "Pocket reality"/"Reality bubble" Pick one.}{Reality Marble!}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.14,0:06:21.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was really dangerous, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.80,0:06:25.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People who are swallowed by that world never return alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.13,0:06:29.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were fighting such a scary enemy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.61,0:06:31.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, staking my life on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.20,0:06:35.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why the two of you should think this over carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.85,0:06:38.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You two, chosen by Kyubei,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.19,0:06:43.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,given an opportunity to fulfill any dream, would you be willing to face death at any time?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.14,0:06:47.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a difficult decision, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.63,0:06:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore, I have an idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.69,0:06:54.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you accompany me in vanquishing Witches for a while?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.91,0:06:57.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In doing so, you will come to understand what exactly it means to be a Magical Girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.41,0:06:59.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Use your very own eyes to verify
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.69,0:07:04.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,whether your dreams need to be fulfilled at the risk of your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.64,0:07:07.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You need to consider this seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.89,0:07:12.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.38,0:07:13.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.65,0:07:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morn—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.53,0:07:16.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Sayaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.10,0:07:20.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong, Sayaka-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.23,0:07:24.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it really true that only we can see this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.35,0:07:25.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems so.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.05,0:07:29.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing, let's go, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.72,0:07:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that we can communicate with each other if we speak in our mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.36,0:07:40.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have magical powers already?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.60,0:07:44.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, you're just communicating through me for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.77,0:07:47.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But isn't it convenient to be able to talk secretly?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.04,0:07:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It feels really weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.40,0:07:53.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on between you two?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.80,0:07:55.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You keep staring at each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.20,0:07:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.85,0:08:01.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me the two of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.41,0:08:04.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,have already reached the point where you can understand each other with just your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.49,0:08:08.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's only been a day, and you've already progressed to this point so quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.76,0:08:11.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What exactly happened yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.16,0:08:13.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how you look at it, you're exaggerating.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.72,0:08:16.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although a lot of things {\i1}did{\i0} happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.43,0:08:20.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you two can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.25,0:08:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Both of you are female.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.90,0:08:25.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a forbidden romance!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.77,0:08:27.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You dropped your bag!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.29,0:08:33.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hitomi-chan seemed just like Sayaka-chan today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.11,0:08:35.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.90,0:08:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it really okay to come with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.89,0:08:51.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.01,0:08:52.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I already told you,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.40,0:08:55.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that person yesterday was a transfer student who's in this class.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.96,0:08:58.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't she try to take your life?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.32,0:09:01.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think school might actually be safer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.22,0:09:02.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mami is here too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.52,0:09:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mami is a third-year, so her classroom is pretty far away from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.40,0:09:09.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, I can hear your voices.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.83,0:09:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The distance is still within the range of telepathy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.12,0:09:16.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.40,0:09:19.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, I'll watch over you properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.65,0:09:23.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That girl doesn't want to attract much attention to herself either.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.91,0:09:25.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it's okay then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.74,0:09:29.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Speak of the devil.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.05,0:09:40.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That transfer student is also a... Magical Girl was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.09,0:09:41.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like Mami-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.59,0:09:43.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, there's no doubt about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.86,0:09:45.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems she also possesses great power.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.99,0:09:47.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if that's the case,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.16,0:09:49.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,shouldn't she be helping the righteous side dealing with the Witches?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.86,0:09:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would she suddenly attack Madoka?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.90,0:09:55.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was her target.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.69,0:09:59.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She probably wanted to prevent more Magical Girls from being born.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.74,0:10:01.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.78,0:10:05.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since we're fighting a common enemy, wouldn't it be better to have more allies?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.77,0:10:11.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, looking at it from another perspective, wouldn't it increase the competitiveness of the battles?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.03,0:10:13.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way, why's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.34,0:10:16.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you defeat a Witch, you can obtain the reward you are promised.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.08,0:10:22.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So sometimes, due to the circumstances, we will find ourselves in conflict with each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.85,0:10:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So basically, she already knew that Kyubei would make Madoka an offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.60,0:10:31.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So she came to stop us beforehand?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.27,0:10:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm afraid that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.32,0:10:41.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mind her, Madoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.13,0:10:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If she tries to make a move, I'll beat her up. {TLC Note: "Beat her up"}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.50,0:10:47.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, Mami-san is on our side.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.61,0:10:50.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, Miki-san aside, I'm here too,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.28,0:10:53.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so don't be afraid, there's nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.62,0:10:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to say "Miki-san aside."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.38,0:11:02.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So then, those which express actions or control are "active voice,"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.68,0:11:04.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,while the opposite is called "passive voice."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.76,0:11:10.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For example, if B, because of A, was made to do something
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.08,0:11:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and exhibits the characteristics of receiving orders or being controlled, this defines "passive voice." {I have no clue where in the hell to split this up}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.79,0:11:18.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B verb and past tense.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.23,0:11:21.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For example, "He likes me," does he like me?{"He likes me" is actually active voice, but whatever}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.99,0:11:24.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.41,0:11:33.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, have you thought about what wish you would want granted, Madoka?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.62,0:11:36.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not really, and you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.25,0:11:37.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.29,0:11:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking, even though we can easily come up with loads of wishes,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.07,0:11:47.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a lot of things we want or would like to do,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.35,0:11:50.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't think of anything I'd like risking my life for to have granted.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.19,0:11:54.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't seem necessary to risk your life all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.15,0:11:59.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is really surprising, a lot of kids would agree immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.35,0:12:03.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're probably just being stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.03,0:12:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that what it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.40,0:12:08.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep, lucky idiots. {TLC Note: "happy idiots"}{TL Note: JP: Shiawase, CH: Xing fu}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.55,0:12:15.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not really surprising. The world must have a lot of people who have dreams...{ this world must have alot of people who have them.}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.46,0:12:21.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for which they would risk their life to have them granted.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.38,0:12:27.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why it's fitting to say that those of us who can't see our destination
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.09,0:12:29.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,don't understand that kind of pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.67,0:12:34.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've become idiots because we've received so much kindness.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.70,0:12:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why us?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.98,0:12:41.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This doesn't seem fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.07,0:12:47.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This chance should be given to those who really need it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.51,0:12:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sayaka-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.55,0:12:57.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.59,0:13:09.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want a repeat of yesterday's incident?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.31,0:13:11.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I have no such plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.27,0:13:16.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to settle this before this thing met Madoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.88,0:13:18.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that it has come to this, it's too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.17,0:13:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what do you intend to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.36,0:13:25.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to become Magical Girls, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.65,0:13:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.57,0:13:30.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have to tell you anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.96,0:13:34.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember what I said yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.81,0:13:35.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.96,0:13:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.40,0:13:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I trust my warning won't be wasted on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.34,0:13:43.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Homura-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.08,0:13:48.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you become a Magical Girl to fulfill some wish?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.63,0:14:14.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Hitomi, we both have something to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.22,0:14:16.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something secret?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.69,0:14:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so envious!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.30,0:14:24.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your relationship has reached a point where you don't want interference!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.92,0:14:28.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it isn't like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.20,0:14:34.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to go to the coffee shop with us after school, Akemi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.55,0:14:37.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have something to do today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.61,0:14:38.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.26,0:14:48.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, this is the first phase of Magical Girl lessons.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.25,0:14:50.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.76,0:14:51.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you prepared?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.99,0:14:54.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really know whether we're adequately prepared,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.80,0:14:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I brought this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.62,0:15:01.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems better than not bringing anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.01,0:15:04.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, if we end up in such a tough situation that we would need to use that, it'll be a great help.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.86,0:15:06.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you bring, Madoka?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.03,0:15:10.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.65,0:15:21.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking we should decide on costumes first.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.98,0:15:29.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really did put some effort into this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.99,0:15:33.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I surrender, you've beaten me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.03,0:15:43.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This shows the traces of magic left by the Witch from yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.53,0:15:46.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Simply put, it's the only way to find a Witch.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.61,0:15:50.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By using the Soul Gem{TLC Note: "Soul Gem"} like this, we can track the Witch down.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.01,0:15:52.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's surprisingly simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.17,0:16:01.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The light hasn't changed at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.09,0:16:04.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a night since the Witch fled the scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.35,0:16:06.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The traces are weakening.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.37,0:16:09.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If only we had gone after her back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.32,0:16:11.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even then, we wouldn't necessarily have been able to handle her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.99,0:16:15.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, my priority at the time was to protect you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.00,0:16:18.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.16,0:16:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.13,0:16:22.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mami-san really is on the side of righteousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.65,0:16:25.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,compared to that transfer student.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.27,0:16:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It really makes me mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.62,0:16:32.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is she really a bad person?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.81,0:16:49.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Mami-san, we don't have a way to find the Witch if she isn't here, do we?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.12,0:16:55.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The most common incidents after a person has been cursed are traffic accidents and explosions.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.26,0:17:00.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore, we'd first check the main roads and most dangerous shopping districts.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.50,0:17:04.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also places where people are likely to commit suicide; dark, isolated places.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.96,0:17:09.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it would be bad if they were somewhere like a hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.72,0:17:15.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By absorbing energy from those who are already weak, their condition would worsen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.14,0:17:21.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A strong wave of magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.77,0:17:24.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It should be very close.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.36,0:17:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no doubt about it, it's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.04,0:17:37.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, Mami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.34,0:17:59.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Witch's love bite...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.42,0:18:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It really {\i1}is{\i0} like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.16,0:18:03.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is she...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.34,0:18:05.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay, she just fainted.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.50,0:18:07.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.87,0:18:22.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you escape today.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.58,0:18:27.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.19,0:18:32.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though it's not much of use for fighting, it might help you protect yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.13,0:18:35.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must not leave my side.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.38,0:18:36.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.07,0:18:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't come here, don't come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.12,0:19:00.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How is it? You two are scared, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.39,0:19:03.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.67,0:19:18.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm scared, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.08,0:19:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, we're almost at the heart of this realm.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.22,0:19:50.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, it's a Witch.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.83,0:19:54.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.15,0:19:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do we have to fight that thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.00,0:20:01.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, I won't lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.64,0:20:06.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stand back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.62,0:20:51.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.93,0:20:59.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, I won't lose face in front of my future juniors.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.92,0:21:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.41,0:21:22.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finale!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.89,0:21:39.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We won?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.86,0:21:40.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.77,0:21:51.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a grief seed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.60,0:21:52.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a Witch's egg.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.96,0:21:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Egg?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.50,0:21:58.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Witches will drop these when they perish if we're lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.47,0:22:01.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, it's safe right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.82,0:22:03.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, it's a very useful treasure in battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.88,0:22:08.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My Soul Gem's {TLC Note: "Soul Gem}color is a little duller than yesterday, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.97,0:22:10.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems so.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.26,0:22:12.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if we use the grief seed...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.16,0:22:14.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.67,0:22:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It regained its luster.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.35,0:22:22.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See? If we do this, my magic will be restored.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.72,0:22:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the reward I mentioned for vanquishing a Witch.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.31,0:22:34.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It should still have one use left.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.30,0:22:41.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can have it, Akemi Homura-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.17,0:22:42.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's her.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.01,0:22:47.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or are you saying you're not happy that I'm sharing it with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.22,0:22:51.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You earned this yourself, so you should keep it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.61,0:22:57.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's your answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.59,0:23:04.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She really pisses me off.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.54,0:23:06.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If only we could make up with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.65,0:23:09.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we'd need her to think that way too.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.42,0:23:18.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is... I'm...?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.97,0:23:21.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.47,0:23:24.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would I do...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.30,0:23:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would I do such a thing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.46,0:23:28.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, it's all right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.22,0:23:32.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just had a nightmare, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.50,0:23:36.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess this wraps things up.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.70,0:23:40.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A wish to be fulfilled...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.07,0:23:45.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's still hard for me to decide right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.84,0:23:51.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Mami-san's silhouette looked magnificent when she saved her.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.96,0:24:03.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If someone like me could become like her and help others, I would be really happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.00,0:24:19.81,NEXT EPISODE TITLE,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0.6\blur3\fs30\c&HF8F7FF&\fnArial\3c&H03050B&\fscy90\pos(1076,640.5)}Mizukawa Hekiru
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.71,0:24:11.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forcing yourself to face it, even when you're scared or in pain,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.22,0:24:15.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or when no one is there to help you and you want to hide and cry...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.97,0:24:19.81,NEXT EPISODE TITLE,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(527,0)\an1\blur5\pos(334,444)}Episode 3  I'm Not Afraid of Anything
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.22,0:24:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The life of a Magical Girl isn't easy!
